About
-----
SAINT Security Suite Add-on for Splunk is a small add-on
for creating a datatype suitable for use with the HTTP event collector
data input which is how SAINT transfers data to Splunk.

Version Support
---------------
Splunk 6.2 or higher
SAINT Security Suite 9.7 or higher

Installation and Configuration
------------------------------
Follow the instructions at these two links.
http://my.saintcorporation.com/resources/documentation/help/saint9_help/configurations.htm#Splunk
http://my.saintcorporation.com/resources/documentation/help/saint9_help/analyze.html#Export_to_Splunk

Troubleshooting
---------------
Contact the SAINT Support Team by logging in to your account
at https://my.saintcorporation.com

